{"word":"χερμάδιον","slug":"χερμάδιον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n113794\" key=\"xerma/dion\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">χερμ-άδιον</orth> <pron extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pron\">[ᾰ]</pron>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, <sense id=\"n113794.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">large stone, boulder,</tr_> such as were used for missiles by the heroes of the <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author></bibl>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὀκριόεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:518\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.518</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μεγάλα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:265\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.265</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:14:410\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.410</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὁ δὲ χερμάδιον λάβε χειρὶ . . , μέγα ἔργον, ὃ οὐ δύο γ᾽ ἄνδρε φέροιεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:302\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.302</biblScope></bibl></cit>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:20:285\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20.285</biblScope> </bibl>; twice in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author></bibl>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀνδραχθέσι χερμαδίοισι βάλλον,</foreign> of the Laestrygones, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:10:121\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.121</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:21:371\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.371</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n113794.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">χερμάς</ref> </xr> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1</biblScope></bibl>, Aen. Tact.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:38:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">38.6</biblScope></bibl>.—Not a <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dim\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\">Dim. of</gram> </gramGrp> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">χερμάς,</foreign> but neut. of an <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adj.\">Adj.</a></pos> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">χερμάδιος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">of the shape</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">size of a</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">χερμάς, μολύβδαιναι χερμάδιοι</foreign> leaden balls <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">for arm-exercises,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg046:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lex.\">Lex.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}